&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Aspiring Emergency Practitioner, Emergency Department&lt;/strong&gt; – Hampshire Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Basingstoke and North Hampshire Hospitals&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking to progress your career as an Emergency Practitioner? Are you a Band 6 who would you like to join a team that will help you develop into a band 7?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interested&lt;/strong&gt;? Then read on or even better come and visit us and find out more about working with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A bit more information about what you can expect:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong in-house education programme with active partnership in the Wessex Emergency care collaborative (WECC), accredited by Health Education Wessex School of Emergency Medicine&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regular staff meetings and the opportunity to participate in on-going education and research to support continuing self-development. In house clinical educators on shift&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An opportunity to gain experience and develop as an autonomous practitioner within a well lead supportive environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide high quality of evidence based care for all our patients in the Emergency department and other Emergency care settings as appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A chance to act as a role model for clinical staff within the Emergency Department&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;initiate and lead nursing initiatives within HHFT, contributing to the successful delivery of both HHFT and national targets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To find out more about the role please read the attached JD and person spec. For informal questions and to book a visit please contact Alison Watts alison.watts@hhft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible working patterns will considered for all nursing applicants!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Come and visit our Instagram takeover 12th October - @hampshirehospitals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alison Watts - Lead ENP&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;alison.watts@hhft.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
